要启用，可用借助 dconf-editor 工具，打开 dconf-editor，展开 org.gnome.shell ，将 user-theme 插件加入到键值 enabled-extensions 中

['user-theme@gnome-shell-extensions.gcampax.github.com', 'poweroptions@fpmurphy.com']

当然，user-theme 插件需要自己下载


sudo pacman -S gnome-shell-extension-user-theme




启用了插件后，重启 gnome-shell


<Alt+F2>

r<Enter>



gnome-shell-theme-atolm.noarch

gnome-shell-theme-dark-glass.noarch

gnome-shell-theme-gaia.noarch

gnome-shell-theme-orta.noarch

gnome-shell-theme-smooth-inset.noarch
